{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2b16285939","title":"对武等县关于追脏的几项政策规定的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c7cd420aa0","index":0,"year":1952,"month":3,"day":9,"articleId":"2b16285939"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"8dee14c96c","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"2b16285939","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共平原省委1952年3月4日关于武陆等县正确贯彻政策追交姓物脏款给各地委、市委、县委并报华北局的通报。通报介绍的武陆等县关于追退脏物姓款的几项政策规定是：“现存姓款、姓物，立即交出：不便于立即交出者（如投资尚未结账等），可先交证件；原物已消耗者可登记，开清单，确实挥霍掉者，本人申请，群众评议，听候领导处理。追姓中不准损伤他人（如亲属）财产，更不准封门，停业，不准通供等。”"}],"contents":[{"id":"cd0c91fe42","type":"title","text":"对武等县关于追脏的几项政策规定的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"2b16285939"},{"id":"8dee14c96c","type":"paragraph","text":"此件很好，请各级党委一律照办。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"2b16285939"},{"id":"172ef920ef","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"2b16285939"},{"id":"0d3fda8630","type":"paragraph","text":"三月九日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"2b16285939"}],"page":{"id":"a24f0a5b1a","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"2b16285939","start":498,"end":498}}}},"__N_SSG":true}